{"tid":2396713,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"貓肉食譜","createTime":"2021-02-05T22:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T14:01:18.000Z","uid":22692,"like":4,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9c65e014c19f6d4236d685d0da00de77b67055","tid":2396713,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T22:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">切勿係香港煮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冬笋焗猫肉<br />\n<br />\n材料<br />\n猫肉件250克，冬笋200克，蒜茸10克，湿陈皮1克，姜米2.5克，姜汁酒10克，油味料等适量。<br />\n<br />\n做法<br />\n1、先将猫肉件滚过，倾在疏壳里，沥干水分。<br />\n2、将冬笋切为榄形件滚过。<br />\n3、用油起镬，将蒜茸、姜米、湿陈皮、滚过的猫件放在镬中爆透，淋入姜汁酒炒匀，注入二汤，用精盐、味粉调味，用深色酱油调成金黄色泽，加盖焗至八成（火念），加入冬笋抛匀，待（火念），撒入胡椒粉，用湿淀粉打芡，加包尾油、麻油和匀，放在煲中便成。"},{"pid":"3029e8384acf8985116d0fc6ac1b1a7acbbe32ea","tid":2396713,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T22:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2a2e4b05309a570ac3704704f4683a6921959d","tid":2396713,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T22:41:08.000Z","msg":"幫推，高汁PO"},{"pid":"6ff42a0a41c86d2af31803b6d97aaefd23c96282","tid":2396713,"uid":329977,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T22:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oDo1waW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoDo1waW.gif&h=285d630e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36536d4945a87b2cce55114d89611ba42e17f4cb","tid":2396713,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3a2a2e4b05309a570ac3704704f4683a6921959d","tid":2396713,"uid":30076,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T22:41:08.000Z","msg":"幫推，高汁PO"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"你係咪都想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"